entity.name: VCOUNTOPORTFROMYEAR
entity.ddl:
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW VCOUNTOPORTFROMYEAR AS SELECT a.ETAPA as ETAPA,DATE_PART('year', ALTA) AS Year,DATE_PART('month', ALTA) AS Month,Count ( aa.IDXOPORTUNIDAD )  as IDXOPORTUNIDAD,Sum ( aa.IMPORTEFINAL )  as IMPORTEFINAL,Sum ( aa.IMPORTEPREV )  as IMPORTEPREV FROM CRMOPORTUNIDAD aa
 INNER JOIN 
CRMPIPELINE ab ON ab.IDXCRMPIPELINE = aa.IDCRMPIPELINE0 INNER JOIN 
CRMETAPA a ON a.IDXCRMETAPA = aa.IDCRMETAPA0
 GROUP BY ETAPA,DATE_PART('year', ALTA),DATE_PART('month', ALTA);
